Package: clinconcept
Type: Package
Title: A package for loading and querying clinical concept dictionaries in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rob Free
Maintainer: Rob Free <rcfree@protonmail.com>
Description: clinconcept is a package which provides tools to work with clinical concept dictionaries by enabling researchers to simply build local or remote databases
  using UK National Health Service (NHS) based concept dictionary downloads; and then query terms directly or through hierarchical/graphs-based relationships.
  Supported by this tool are NHS-based downloads of READ versions 2 and 3, SNOMED-CT and ICD10.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
